\b\fs28 1. Intended use of the system: who and how will use the system?\

\b0\fs24 The intended users for this system are: \
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural
\ls1\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\'95	}People with internet access looking to view live data on a computer or mobile device.\
{\listtext	\'95	}People traveling within the New Britain/Hartford area.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural
\ls2\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\'95	}People without cars.\
{\listtext	\'95	}People commuting to and from work.\
{\listtext	\'95	}Responsible college students enjoying the night life.\
\pard\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\pardirnatural
\cf0 \
The system will primarily be used for these actions:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural
\ls3\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\'95	}Getting locations - Looking up where the nearest bus to individual is, getting an individual\'92s location and comparing it to the nearest arriving bus.\
{\listtext	\'95	}Setting destinations - Users deciding where to go use the system to figure out at which stops to get on and off.\
{\listtext	\'95	}Picking routes - The system will provide multiple options for routes based on destinations and bus availability. The optimal route is displayed first.\
{\listtext	\'95	}Getting bus information - The system can provide information about bus number, arrival/departure time, current location, etc.\
{\listtext	\'95	}Getting bus stop info - The system will provide information about bus stop locations, next arrival, and next departure times for stops.\
{\listtext	\'95	}Displaying notifications - In the situation that a bus is broken down, delayed, or a time change or other event, the system will notify the user via some type of message (whether it be on the web app, email, etc).\
\pard\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\pardirnatural
\cf0 \
A typical use case includes:\
A rider is looking for the information described above (locations, destinations, routes, bus and bus stop information, and notifications).\
A map API takes care of location and route information and calculates route data to display to the user.\
A GTFS feed provides notifications for real-time changes or updates based on traffic and bus conditions.\
\

\b\fs28 2. Its overall functionality: what will the system do, how will the system help its users accomplish their tasks?\

\b0\fs24 The system will provide live and accurate information with real-time notifications to allow users to plan an optimal transit route via the CTFastTrak system. The system will visually display CTFastTrak data in a meaningful way for users and do calculations on top of the CTFastTrak data and map data in order to plan the optimal user route based on the user\'92s given parameters.\
\

