\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural
\ls4\ilvl0
\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	1.	}The map API and tools for the visual representation of data. - This is a big component that has to be learned and integrated with the data from CTFastTrak.\
{\listtext	2.	}The GTFS data for real-time updates from the system. - This is the most valuable data set from CTFastTrak that has to be designed with proper notifications on mobile.\
{\listtext	3.	}The JSON data for information about the system. - The backbone of the system that allows the user to get bus information.\
{\listtext	4.	}The client-side interface for the user (both computer and mobile responsive). - The component that requires visual and design work and needs to provide a smooth user experience.}